  "Description": {
    "English": "Equip this exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Personal Flair</span> in commemoration of the 'Cartographers' <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Expedition</span>, and your success in documenting and then escaping from the expedition planet.<br><br>Apply this banner to your profile at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "装备上这枚专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">个人旗帜</span>，纪念你完成了“制图师”<span class=\"name name-stellar\">远征</span>，以及成功记录并逃离了远征行星。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>中将这面旗帜应用至你的个人档案。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "裝備這款獨家的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">個人造型</span>紀念完成「地圖學家」<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探險</span>，且成功拍攝紀錄並從探險行星逃離的成就。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>將此旗幟套用至你的檔案。"
  },
